							<div class="box-border content-stretch flex flex-col gap-6 items-start justify-start p-0 relative shrink-0 w-full">
								<div class="font-['Mona_Sans',_sans-serif] font-semibold leading-[0] min-w-full not-italic relative shrink-0 text-[#242c39] text-[48px] text-left" style="width: min-content">
									<p class="block leading-none">
										Savvy Pet Mobile Apps Are Here!
									</p>
								</div>
								<div class="font-['Mona_Sans',_sans-serif] font-normal leading-[0] min-w-full not-italic relative shrink-0 text-[#656689] text-[16px] text-left" style="width: min-content">
									<p class="block leading-[30px]">
										We've built two apps—one for groomers, and one for their customers. Groomers can manage their day-to-day with ease, while customers can book, pay, and stay updated—all from their phone.
									</p>
								</div>
								<div class="box-border content-stretch flex flex-row gap-6 items-center justify-start p-0 relative shrink-0">
									<div class="h-[56.826px] overflow-clip relative shrink-0 w-[170px]">
										<div class="absolute contents inset-0">
											<div class="absolute contents inset-0">
												<div class="absolute inset-0">
													<img alt="" class="block max-w-none size-full" loading="lazy" src="/f4e5dd292614d49a5ebe9d67f848360312f13db4.svg" />
												</div>
											</div>
										</div>
									</div>
